#: ../../mail/configuration-server.rst:352
msgid ""
"The |UCSUCRV|\\ s :envvar:`mail/dovecot/limits`\\ ``/*`` can be set to "
"modify the limits. The process of adapting those variables is only semi "
"automatic, because of their complex interaction. For the meaning of each "
"variable refer to `Dovecot Wiki: Service configuration <dovecot-"
"services_>`_."
