"``default_process_limit`` do not only lift limits for IMAP and POP3, but "
"also for other services like ``lmtp`` and ``managesieve-login``. Those "
"services can now start more processes that have to be monitored and can "
"theoretically make more authentication requests. This increases the "
"number of possible concurrent connections to the ``auth`` and ``anvil`` "
"services."
